=Description=

"Stacco Troncoso presents the P2P Foundation's work as a digital community researching and advocating for the P2P/Commons movement.

This talk was part of the Prix Ars Festival 2016, held in Linz, Austria. The P2P Foundation was awarded the Golden Nica award for Digital Communities."


